## üîÑ Future Update Process

### For New Versions (1.0.2, 1.1.0, etc.)

#### 1. Update Version Numbers

```bash
# Update package.json
npm version patch  # for 1.0.2
npm version minor  # for 1.1.0
npm version major  # for 2.0.0

# Update manifest.json version to match
```

#### 2. Rebuild Extension

```bash
npm run build
```

#### 3. Create New ZIP File

```bash
cd dist
zip -r ../mayday-bar-extension-v1.0.2.zip .
```

#### 4. Chrome Web Store Update

1. Go to [Chrome Web Store Developer Dashboard](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/devconsole/)
2. Select "Mayday Bar" extension
3. Go to "Package" section
4. Upload new ZIP file
5. Update release notes in "Store listing" section
6. Submit for review

#### 5. Update Release Notes Template

```
Version X.X.X - [Update Type]
‚Ä¢ [New feature 1]
‚Ä¢ [New feature 2]
‚Ä¢ [Bug fix 1]
‚Ä¢ [Bug fix 2]
‚Ä¢ [Performance improvement]
‚Ä¢ [Security update]
```

### Update Checklist

