#### Publishing to Chrome Store

- Increment package version
- cd chrome-softphone-extension && npm run build
- cd dist && zip -r ../mayday-bar-extension-v1.0.1.zip .
- Go to Chrome Web Store Developer Dashboard ~ https://chrome.google.com/webstore/devconsole/
- Click "Add new item"
- Upload the mayday-bar-extension-v1.0.1.zip file
